I feel like visitors tend to overhype their 'exotic' street food experience, so I went there to see if it really is as good as people say.

Is Gwangjang Market really the best place for street food in Korea?

snippet.title: This is Korea's MOST POPULAR Food. (Really)
snippet.description:
This might surprise some people, but fried chicken is probably the most popular food in South Korea. We love it so much that we have more fried chicken restaurants in Korea than the number of McDonald locations in the entire world!

So what makes it so great? Let uncle Jimmy show you, because I went to my father's rural farm in South Korea to cook fried chicken myself from scratch.

Corn Syrup 3 tbsp (You can use honey or just more sugar)

snippet.title: I Made World's Most Popular Liquor at Home.
snippet.description:

I'm also going to cook some authentic Korean dinner to go with the home made liquor.
